snippet.title: [Otome Game] Kago no Naka no Alicis  Demo  Part 1 (CC English Subs)
snippet.description:
CC for subtitles, part 2 will come out when ever I have time. I'll only be translating up to the end of the demo. Let me know if you notice any mistakes I missed and I'll edit the subtitles.
